<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Alhamdu ga Allah Don Ɗansa, Yesu LW133</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Alhamdu ga Allah don Ɗansa, Yesu.
 Ya ba da jininsa domin fansarmu,
 Amma dai ya tashi, ya koma Sammai.
 Ya kan ba da Ruhu, da yawan kyautai.

[V2]
 KORUS
 Madalla! Madlla! bari kowa ya ji.
 Madalla! Madalla! dukan kowa ya bi.
 Ku zo wurin Allah ta wurin Yesu,
 Yi masa godiya don Mai Cetonmu.

[V3]
 2) Ya ceto cikakke, kyautar Allahnmu!
 Kowane mai tuba, mai ba da gaskiya,
 Kowane mai laifi, kome laifinsa,
 In ya zo gun Yesu zai sami gafara.
 Korus

[V4]
 3) Mu kuwa waƙar yabo ce mu ke ta yi.
 Ga Allah don Ɗansa, shi ne masoyi.
 Amma za mu ƙara yin murna sarai,
 Sa'ad da muka gan shi da ido sosai.
 Korus</lyrics>
<hymn_number>133</hymn_number>
<author>Doane, William Howard (1832-1915), Crosby, Fanny Jane (1820-1915)</author>
</song>